Class RecordTokenWritable

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<org.apache.hadoop.io.BinaryComparable>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable, org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<org.apache.hadoop.io.BinaryComparable>

    public class RecordTokenWritable
extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Text
    A Writable for Ptolemy record tokens. Record tokens are serialized as strings, so this class inherits all methods from StringValue. This class is necessary to differentiate strings and records.
    Author:
    Daniel Crawl
